Missing values by variable

skimr::skim()

skimr::skim(mycars) %>% filter(stat == "missing") %>% 
  arrange(desc(value)) %>% select(variable, type, value) %>% mutate(percent = value/nrow(mycars))

NYC School data

Looking for patterns in missing data

value patterns

  • Are missing patterns correlated with values of another variable?
    (MAR = missing at random)
  • Are certain (true) value ranges more likely to be missing?
    (MNAR = missing not at random)
  • Or are there no patterns at all?
    (MCAR = missing completely at random)
